30:27.434 --> 30:29.610
- Curriculum? Schedule?

30:29.653 --> 30:32.221
Not what you're expecting, huh?

30:32.265 --> 30:36.573
- That stock image on your
website was a nice touch.

30:36.617 --> 30:39.402
When can I meet the kids?

30:39.446 --> 30:40.403
- Stop.

30:40.447 --> 30:42.841
[speaks in Spanish]

30:42.884 --> 30:44.755
- Man.

30:44.799 --> 30:45.974
