little bit of Spanish,

30:46.018 --> 30:47.541
think she the mom of us.

30:47.584 --> 30:48.759
- Oh my gosh, shut up.
[Jaylen laughs]

30:48.803 --> 30:49.891
- Guys.

30:49.935 --> 30:50.761
- [Jalen] All I'm sayin' is-

30:50.805 --> 30:52.502
- Guys.

30:52.546 --> 30:54.940
This is Ms. Grace.

30:54.983 --> 30:56.202
- That's the lady I saw.

30:56.245 --> 30:57.681
- She's here to
teach you music.

30:57.725 --> 30:59.248
- Uh uh, this is our
free time Miss K.

30:59.292 --> 31:00.815
- Yeah.

31:00.859 --> 31:02.599
