31:02.643 --> 31:05.385
- Excuse me, I gotta take
this. I'll be right back.

31:05.428 --> 31:07.691
- I aint sign up
for no music class.

31:07.735 --> 31:10.956
- Good, because this
is music therapy.

31:10.999 --> 31:12.871
- We got counselors already.

31:12.914 --> 31:15.743
- Music therapy is
a way for you to

31:15.786 --> 31:19.790
express yourselves creatively,
with all kinds of music.

31:19.834 --> 31:21.662
- Like you want us to sing?

31:21.705 --> 31:22.924
[sucks teeth]

31:22.968 --> 31:23.751
- Nobody asked
you to sing.

31:23.794 --> 31:24.795
[laughing]

31:24.839 --> 31:26.580
- [Jalen] You so rude.

31:26.623 --> 31:28.930
- There aren't really any
rules to this kind of music.

31:28.974 --> 31:31.411
- Sounds like a waste of time.

31:31.454 --> 31:33.630
- Well could you please
hold your opinion

31:33.674 --> 31:36.546
until you find out
what it's all about?

31:36.590 --> 31:39.332
[laughing]

31:39.375 --> 31:40.246
- Yo.

31:40.289 --> 31:41.595
Yo?

31:41.638 --> 31:43.423
King of Devlin. I'm
back, what's up?

31:43.466 --> 31:46.382
- My boy, welcome back.
- What's up, what's up?

31:46.426 --> 31:47.209
What's good, dog?

31:47.253 --> 31:49.081
[hits]

31:49.124 --> 31:50.952
[laughing]

31:50.996 --> 31:53.694
Aye.
- That's not funny, bro.

31:53.737 --> 31:54.782
