35:22.598 --> 35:24.165
- Good afternoon.

35:26.036 --> 35:27.908
- [Q] You know it is.

35:29.779 --> 35:31.912
- No coffee today?

35:31.955 --> 35:33.653
- I can't get with this.

35:33.696 --> 35:34.567
- Run that.

35:34.610 --> 35:35.916
- It's trash.

35:35.959 --> 35:37.222
- What?
- It's trash.

35:37.265 --> 35:38.223
- That is not trash.

35:38.266 --> 35:39.746
